name: Employee Resource Groups
description:
Employee resource groups are groups of underrepresented and/or marginalized employees who join together in the workplace based on shared characteristics or life experiences. ERGs are generally based on providing support, enhancing career development, and contributing to personal development in the work environment.
ERGs differ from informal clubs in that they speak to an individual's identity and how that has affected their daily lives and speak to Diversity & Inclusion.
